		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Secret of Evermore isn't known to use any form of anti-piracy. Atleast UCON64 doesn't crack it and it cracks most if not all SRAM based anti piracy as well as a few of the Capcom ROM based ones.
<br />
<br />Do you have to go far into the game to save? If I have time I'll try it out. I can't think of any good reason why it wouldn't work properly unless it is detecting header information wrong.

		

