	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sounds to me like a software (read: 65816 code in the ROM/game itself) checksum problem of some sort -- lots of games can suffer from this issue.
<br />
<br />There is no evidence to suggest it's an anti-piracy effort, so that should be considered complete FUD at this point in time.  Please don't go that route.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


